userinterface.util

Interface GUIGroupedTableModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javax.swing.table.TableModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GUISimulatorPathTableModel

    public interface GUIGroupedTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.TableModel
    An interface which extends TableModel such that also group information can be extracted automatically. Note that groups are always non-empty.
